The SOFTWARE is defined as all successive versions of NIRS-KIT software and their documentation that have been developed by the authors.
NIRS-KIT DERIVED SOFTWARE is defined as all or part of the SOFTWARE that you have modified and/or translated and/or adapted.
NIRS-KIT COMPOSITE SOFTWARE is defined as all or a part of the SOFTWARE that you have interfaced with the software, an application package or a toolbox of which you are the owner or entitled beneficiary.

